ku: k with framebuffer + key & mouse

build
$wget https://github.com/ktye/i/releases/download/latest/k.c
$sed '/^int main/Q k.c                                  >k.h
$sh mk                               (compile ku.c on linux)
$sh mk w                           (compile ku.c on windows)


k interface: 
 W:H:(size)  K:{[key]}  (paint):P[color;indexlist]


$ku x.k
$ku 2 x.k        (scaled)

W:H:200          /window size
B:P 255          /blue
G:P 255*256      /green
R:P 255*256*256  /red

K:{P[10*x;!W*H]} /key callback
